name: Asymmetrical Liberation
description:
Genesis Period. 2021 Oct #000.
Asymmetrical Liberation is a planet in
the Synedrion system. It’s a planet
with a single moon, the surface
covered with blue seas and green
landmasses. Countless stars can be
seen in the sky. This planet is full of
people who are trapped by their own
self-created prisons, their fears, their
self-doubts, their own inability to see
the world as it is, the way it could be,
the way it should be. Botto in
conversation with GPT-3.
